00:37:01.640 --> 00:37:03.316
which I think is incredible.

00:37:03.316 --> 00:37:04.940
He talked about the
fact that he thinks

00:37:04.940 --> 00:37:09.080
that there is such a
deficit of love and people

00:37:09.080 --> 00:37:11.810
who are willing to be
vulnerable and that he's

00:37:11.810 --> 00:37:17.450
trying to help people build
a comfort level with that.

00:37:17.450 --> 00:37:20.660
And then he talked
about, hey, I want

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:24.110
to find ways to be more
supportive of what we're doing

00:37:24.110 --> 00:37:26.220
on campus for our athletes.

00:37:26.220 --> 00:37:28.745
And so he's been a supporter.

00:37:28.745 --> 00:37:30.770
He wrote a nice check
to us a few weeks ago.

00:37:30.770 --> 00:37:31.040
ASHLEY CHANG: Yeah,
congratulations.

00:37:31.040 --> 00:37:31.660
This is January.

00:37:31.660 --> 00:37:32.701
DARON ROBERTS: Thank you.

00:37:32.701 --> 00:37:33.230
Thank you.

00:37:33.230 --> 00:37:34.250
ASHLEY CHANG: It
was a nice check.

00:37:34.250 --> 00:37:36.440
It was half a million
dollars that Kevin Durant

00:37:36.440 --> 00:37:38.977
donated to the center
that Daron founded.

00:37:38.977 --> 00:37:40.310
So big congratulations to Daron.

00:37:40.310 --> 00:37:40.650
DARON ROBERTS: Thank you.

00:37:40.650 --> 00:37:41.576
Appreciate it.

00:37:41.576 --> 00:37:42.075
Thank you.

