00:41:29.844 --> 00:41:33.830
So there's a breakfast
taco on every corner,

00:41:33.830 --> 00:41:34.880
but it kind of seems--

00:41:34.880 --> 00:41:35.830
ASHLEY CHANG: It's a
little different, right?

00:41:35.830 --> 00:41:36.650
DARON ROBERTS: It's
a little different.

00:41:36.650 --> 00:41:37.640
It's not quite so pure.

00:41:37.640 --> 00:41:38.300
ASHLEY CHANG: It's
