more and better products

00:54:16.930 --> 00:54:18.820
and ideas and concepts.

00:54:18.820 --> 00:54:20.560
So I first have to
get them to buy in

00:54:20.560 --> 00:54:26.380
that there's this
very real bottom line

00:54:26.380 --> 00:54:29.980
benefit to being and using
vulnerability and empathy.

